<h2 id="问题"><span class="section-num">1</span> 问题</h2>
<p>Elfeed 数据库无法跨设备同步，导致阅读进度不一致。</p>
<h2 id="解决方案"><span class="section-num">2</span> 解决方案</h2>
<p>使用 rclone + 坚果云 WebDAV 实现双向同步。</p>
<h2 id="文件"><span class="section-num">3</span> 文件</h2>
<p><strong><strong>rclone 配置</strong></strong> (<code>~/.dot-files/utils/.config/rclone/rclone.conf</code>)</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span><span class="lnt">5
</span><span class="lnt">6
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-text" data-lang="text"><span class="line"><span class="cl">[jianguoyun]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">type = webdav
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">url = https://dav.jianguoyun.com/dav
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">vendor = jianguoyun
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">user = [YOUR_EMAIL]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">pass = [YOUR_PASSWORD]
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>坚果云支持 WebDAV，通过 rclone 挂载后即可像操作本地文件一样同步。</p>]]></description></item><item><title>罗马人的故事-盐野七生;计丽屏</title><link>https://yangyingchao.github.io/2026/05/%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E7%BD%97%E9%A9%AC%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-%E7%9B%90%E9%87%8E%E4%B8%83%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%BD%E5%B1%8F/</link><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>yc</author><guid>https://yangyingchao.github.io/2026/05/%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E7%BD%97%E9%A9%AC%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-%E7%9B%90%E9%87%8E%E4%B8%83%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%BD%E5%B1%8F/</guid><description></description></item><item><title>西西弗神话_加缪之女亲笔推荐版-[法]阿尔贝·加缪;李玉民</title><link>https://yangyingchao.github.io/2026/05/%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E8%A5%BF%E8%A5%BF%E5%BC%97%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D_%E5%8A%A0%E7%BC%AA%E4%B9%8B%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%B2%E7%AC%94%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E7%89%88-%E6%B3%95%E9%98%BF%E5%B0%94%E8%B4%9D%E5%8A%A0%E7%BC%AA%E6%9D%8E%E7%8E%89%E6%B0%91/</link><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>yc</author><guid>https://yangyingchao.github.io/2026/05/%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E8%A5%BF%E8%A5%BF%E5%BC%97%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D_%E5%8A%A0%E7%BC%AA%E4%B9%8B%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%B2%E7%AC%94%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E7%89%88-%E6%B3%95%E9%98%BF%E5%B0%94%E8%B4%9D%E5%8A%A0%E7%BC%AA%E6%9D%8E%E7%8E%89%E6%B0%91/</guid><description></description></item><item><title>太阳的阴影_深入非洲的旅程-[波] 雷沙德·卡普希钦斯基;毛蕊</title><link>https://yangyingchao.github.io/2026/05/%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E7%9A%84%E9%98%B4%E5%BD%B1_%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%97%85%E7%A8%8B-%E6%B3%A2-%E9%9B%B7%E6%B2%99%E5%BE%B7%E5%8D%A1%E6%99%AE%E5%B8%8C%E9%92%A6%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E6%AF%9B%E8%95%8A/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>yc</author><guid>https://yangyingchao.github.io/2026/05/%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E7%9A%84%E9%98%B4%E5%BD%B1_%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%97%85%E7%A8%8B-%E6%B3%A2-%E9%9B%B7%E6%B2%99%E5%BE%B7%E5%8D%A1%E6%99%AE%E5%B8%8C%E9%92%A6%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E6%AF%9B%E8%95%8A